net.cnri.apps.doserver

Class ConcreteStorageProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cnri.apps.doserver.ConcreteStorageProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RangeRequestStorageProxy, StorageProxy

    public final class ConcreteStorageProxy
extends java.lang.Object
implements RangeRequestStorageProxy
    ConcreteStorageProxy objects provide an interface to the hash-based storage layer of the DO server.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      ConcreteStorageProxy(Storage storage, java.lang.String repositoryID, java.lang.String objectID, HeaderSet txnMetadata)
      Construct a storage accessor/proxy object that uses the given storage mechanism and restricts access to the given objectID based on the permissions granted to the given callerIDs.
